personal.name: Lavi Sharma
personal.intro: Dressing is a way of life. My customers are successful working women. I want people to be afraid of the women I dress. Age is something only in your head or a stereotype. Age means nothing when you are passionate about something. There has to be a balance between your mental satisfaction and the financial needs of your company.
